41, 280.0881, 279.7926, 280.1458, 279.9753, 279.8339, 280.2536, 278.9915, 278.4701, 278.223, 278.173, 278.7331, 279.407, 278.1404, 278.61, 278.8632, 278.4627, 278.5363, 278.7213, 279.2376, 279.5112, 279.025, 278.7145, 278.4015, 278.7551, 278.6475, 278.9558, 279.3899, 280.9167, 280.6251, 282.3068, 281.4514, 281.6112, 282.9675, 281.4775, 281.2558, 281.1984, 281.5284, 282.6374, 281.9215, 280.8902, 280.8387, 282.7027, 280.2274, 280.1131, 279.9188, 279.7046, 280.2476, 280.3139, 280.3454, 280.2233, 281.9084, 281.598, 281.9357, 282.6339, 283.2209, 282.4408, 282.2847, 281.9567, 281.0757, 281.4025, 281.4665, 281.7386, 281.5431, 281.3765, 280.9043, 280.8605, 281.1131, 281.3701, 281.2434, 280.9154, 281.1682, 281.9356, 281.686, 281.7164, 282.1292, 281.0802, 280.5009, 281.1192, 281.447, 280.1023, 279.1165, 279.6305, 280.1815, 279.9137, 280.0077, 279.9582, 280.279, 280.3323, 280.1583, 279.1016, 278.2333, 278.1412, 278.0497, 277.9741, 278.7088, 278.2725, 277.9529, 278.8121, 278.4798, 278.6201, 278.4195, 278.4583, 278.5075, 278.4188, 278.588, 278.4832, 279.3942, 279.2836, 279.0248, 279.4415, 279.5563, 278.9663, 278.4465, 279.2748, 279.2294, 279.5229, 280.1344, 280.7115, 279.4341, 278.8928, 278.3159, 278.3322, 279.109, 277.8612, 278.5497, 278.4593, 279.0136, 279.1761, 279.6054, 280.1998, 280.18, 279.6707, 280.2706, 280.6168, 280.1691, 280.3272, 281.0611, 281.0929, 281.0368, 280.0924, 280.6218, 281.5881, 281.1967, 283.0525, 281.8798, 281.7789, 281.9338, 281.7517, 283.1704, 282.9731, 284.3889, 283.0691, 282.8384, 283.3211, 282.3639, 280.6243, 282.1657, 281.7028, 281.5597, 281.4313, 282.2472, 282.7033, 281.4166, 282.0461, 281.8338, 282.0529, 283.0113, 282.6051, 281.7025, 282.0909, 282.1919, 285.8991, 290.5674, 289.2942, 289.5804, 288.6059, 291.4579, 290.0873, 289.8422, 290.3217, 290.0396, 290.694, 289.9543, 291.0081, 294.643, 293.2436, 292.3738, 291.741, 290.0932, 291.7787, 292.4311, 291.9195, 291.6593, 291.9856, 292.3227, 293.2138, 295.0199, 293.9804, 294.5754, 294.9024, 294.7839, 293.724, 292.8658, 293.0819, 292.4569, 292.4801, 293.4793, 294.0254, 293.833, 293.8075, 293.7018, 294.2403, 295.0333, 295.3191, 294.3487, 294.8655, 296.0906, 296.2049, 297.5056, 297.4685, 296.7724, 297.3169, 297.6688, 298.0194, 298.541, 297.7508, 298.1671, 295.9332, 297.0116, 296.1321, 297.2026, 297.0256, 298.1251, 297.982, 298.8199, 297.7346, 298.3278, 298.7213, 298.4349, 298.3328, 299.0788, 296.5813, 291.8369, 289.1311, 289.6242, 290.2016, 287.6763, 288.194, 286.4443, 284.8897, 284.7549, 285.4053, 285.4492, 283.2611, 282.1618], "summary_html": "<h1>库存水平时序偏离度因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 2.21)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本因子利用商品期货多头库存（<code>inventory_lp</code>）的时序偏离度构建截面多空信号。核心逻辑：当某品种库存水平显著偏离其历史均值（滚动 Z-score 衡量），市场对该品种供需定价可能存在偏差。因子在截面上对所有品种的 Z-score 做百分位排名（库存偏离 → 供需失衡 → 价格回归）。</p>\n<p><strong>实盘变体（OOS 救场后替换）= <code>inv_lp_zs60_h10_novt_icg504_raw</code></strong>（meta.json / index.json 当前部署变体，Sharpe 2.21）。链路为：</p>\n<p>1. 每品种 <code>inventory_lp</code> 的 <strong>60 日时序 Z-score</strong>（<code>inv_zs</code>）； 2. 每日对 <code>inv_zs</code> 做<strong>截面百分位排名</strong> → <code>rank_to_continuous(scale=2)</code> 映射到 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1,1]</span>； 3. <strong>per-sym 滚动 IC 门控</strong>（window=504, min_ic=0，walk-forward 因果掩码）屏蔽近期 IC 为负的品种； 4. <strong>持有 hold=10 日</strong>，<strong>不施加 vol-target</strong>（novt）。</p>\n<p><strong>关键发现（OOS 救场，见 <code>oos_rescue_notes.md</code>）</strong>：初版入库变体 <code>inv_lp_zs100_h1_vt10_raw</code> 的 IS Sharpe 2.25 看似稳健（IS 四分位 1.98–2.74、半样本 2.79/2.54），但 OOS（2025-06 起 198 日）暴跌至 <strong>0.11</strong>，确认<strong>过拟合</strong>——<code>vol_target_scale</code> 是主要过拟合源（关掉后 OOS 从 −0.23→+0.82），zs=100/h=1/vt=0.10 三参数在 IS 期共振。救场结论：<strong>保留因子、替换变体</strong>为 <code>inv_lp_zs60_h10_novt_icg504</code>（去 vol-target + 504 日滚动 IC 门控 + 拉长 hold），其 IS Sharpe 1.34、四分位 0.71–1.68、<strong>OOS 2.19</strong>（自我验证），是综合鲁棒性最优候选。冗余 max_corr 0.40（marginal，最相似 <code>xingye_combo_M90_H3</code>）。</p>\n<blockquote>⚠️ <strong>代码↔元数据漂移（待修，非本任务范围）</strong>：<code>meta.json</code> 与 <code>index.json</code> 已部署 <code>inv_lp_zs60_h10_novt_icg504_raw</code>，但当前 <code>strategy_final.py</code> 的 <code>BEST_VARIANT</code> 仍是旧的 <code>inv_lp_zs100_h1_vt10</code>（zs=100/h=1/vt=0.10），尚未按救场结论同步替换。本摘要按部署变体（meta.json）描述。</blockquote>\n<p><strong>防前视</strong>：<code>inventory_lp</code> 为 T 日披露字段；时序 Z-score 与 IC 门控均为因果窗口，无 <code>shift(-N)</code>/未来数据。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.81</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>8.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-4.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.06</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2537</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.92</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.73</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.85 / 2.04</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.38</span></td><td>0.71</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.23</span></td><td>1.52</td><td>1.96</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.4</span></td><td>0.75</td><td>1.98</td><td>1.32</td><td>1.51</td><td>1.05</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 5 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 5 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>56</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2539</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>44.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>时序 Z-score（窗口 <span class=\"math-tex\">W=60</span>）：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">z_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{inventory\\_lp}_{i,t} - \\mu_{i}^{(W)}}{\\sigma_{i}^{(W)}}</div>\n<p><strong>截面连续信号：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{i,t} = \\big(2\\cdot\\text{cr\\_rank}(z_{i,t}) - 1\\big)\\in[-1,1]</div>\n<p><strong>per-sym 滚动 IC 门控（window=504, min_ic=0）+ 持有：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_{i,t} = \\text{rebalance\\_hold}_{H=10}\\!\\big(\\text{signal}_{i,t}\\cdot g_{i,t}^{\\text{IC,504}}\\big),\\qquad g\\in\\{0,1\\}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">g_{i,t}^{\\text{IC,504}}</span> 为品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 过去 504 日滚动 IC <span class=\"math-tex\">\\ge 0</span> 的因果门控掩码；部署变体<strong>不施加 vol-target</strong>（novt）。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 2.00)</strong>：初始实现，覆盖基准逻辑（inventory_lp zscore -&gt; rank -&gt; continuous signal -&gt; L1 normalize -&gt; vol_target_scale）。参数网格覆盖 zs_window={126,180,252,504}、hold_days={1,5,10,20}、vol_target={0.10,0.15,0.20}，以及 inventory_sp 和 lp+sp 组合变体。意外发现 zs=126（半年窗口）优于基准的 zs=252，inv_lp_zs126_h5_raw 达到 Sharpe 2.00。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 1.94)</strong>：扩展参数空间（加入 zs=63/90），添加 sym_rolling_ic_gate 过滤弱品种，测试 inventory_ln 字段。R2 最优变体 inv_combo_zs126_h5_raw (Sharpe 1.94) 略低于 R1，但验证了信号在不同库存字段间的稳健性。IC-gate 变体与非 gate 变体持平，说明信号在大多数品种上均有效（77% 品种 IC&gt;0）。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 2.21)</strong>：关键突破。在 zs=100/126/150 范围内做细粒度参数网格，同时覆盖 vol_target={0.10,0.15,0.20} 和 hold_days={1,5}。发现低 vol_target (0.10) 配合 hold=1 显著提升 Sharpe（从 2.00 到 2.21），原因是更保守的波动率目标降低了噪声品种的仓位暴露。新增 inventory_sn (Sharpe 1.64) 和 inventory_21 (Sharpe -0.41) 的对比确认了 inventory_lp 是最佳字段。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>主要字段</strong>: inventory_lp（多头库存，非空率约36%总体，近年&gt;90%）</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（56个有库存数据）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每日换仓或5日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 基本面数据（inventory_lp）存在历史NaN，早期品种覆盖率较低\n<p>- 低 vol_target (0.10) 导致绝对收益偏低（年化 4.5%），但风险调整后表现优异 - inventory_21 字段信号为负，不适合此逻辑</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 1.93s</li>\n</ul>"}